{"ja435:0.1":"Jataka ","ja435:0.2":"Navakanipata ","ja435:0.3":"Gijjhavagga ","ja435:0.4":"9. Haliddiragajataka ","ja435:1.1":"“Sutitikkham arannamhi, ","ja435:1.2":"pantamhi sayanasane; ","ja435:1.3":"Ye ca game titikkhanti, ","ja435:1.4":"te ularatara taya”. ","ja435:2.1":"“Aranna gamamagamma, ","ja435:2.2":"kimsilam kimvatam aham; ","ja435:2.3":"Purisam tata seveyyam, ","ja435:2.4":"tam me akkhahi pucchito”. ","ja435:3.1":"“Yo te vissasaye tata, ","ja435:3.2":"vissasanca khameyya te; ","ja435:3.3":"Sussusi ca titikkhi ca, ","ja435:3.4":"tam bhajehi ito gato. ","ja435:4.1":"Yassa kayena vacaya, ","ja435:4.2":"manasa natthi dukkatam; ","ja435:4.3":"Urasiva patitthaya, ","ja435:4.4":"tam bhajehi ito gato. ","ja435:5.1":"Yo ca dhammena carati, ","ja435:5.2":"carantopi na mannati; ","ja435:5.3":"Visuddhakarim sappannam, ","ja435:5.4":"tam bhajehi ito gato. ","ja435:6.1":"Haliddiragam kapicittam, ","ja435:6.2":"purisam ragaviraginam; ","ja435:6.3":"Tadisam tata ma sevi, ","ja435:6.4":"nimmanussampi ce siya. ","ja435:7.1":"Asivisamva kupitam, ","ja435:7.2":"milhalittam mahapatham; ","ja435:7.3":"Araka parivajjehi, ","ja435:7.4":"yaniva visamam patham. ","ja435:8.1":"Anattha tata vaddhanti, ","ja435:8.2":"balam accupasevato; ","ja435:8.3":"Massu balena sangacchi, ","ja435:8.4":"amitteneva sabbada. ","ja435:9.1":"Tam taham tata yacami, ","ja435:9.2":"karassu vacanam mama; ","ja435:9.3":"Massu balena sangacchi, ","ja435:9.4":"dukkho balehi sangamo”ti. ","ja435:10.1":"Haliddiragajatakam navamam. "}